Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.06,OP1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,We Are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.01,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,we're going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:42.45,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:53.84,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:59.27,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,delirious with fever, i take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:05.35,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,if the dusty treasure map has been verified,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:11.22,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:18.09,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,when it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:23.00,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,simply ride aboard someone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:25.89,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:31.73,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,we're going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:37.91,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:41.15,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,a coin in my pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:44.41,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.06,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,we are!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,These are just in the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cat Burglar"...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that great at the One-Sword Style, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.44,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Butchie!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's do it, Siam!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! If I just had another sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can just get Zoro his swords...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need swords for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:43.22,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,115)}Luffy, Back in Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:43.22,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,455)}Miss Kaya's \NDesperate Resistance
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.93,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that these brats have held you back...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How the Black Cat Pirates have fallen...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Jango?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.90,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,B-B-But... you said letting that kid \Ngo wouldn't cause any problems!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.33,0:04:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But so what? \NWe knew he was going to try to stand up to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I didn't count on...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...was you guys' feebleness!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Us, feeble?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling feeble?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch what you say, Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you were strong before!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was three years ago!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.82,0:04:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we partied while you \Nlived the easy life in this village!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.88,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,'As right! We've attacked lotsa \Ntowns and sunk lotsa pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your point being...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.38,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done nothing for three years!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can beat \Nthe Meowban Brothers of today!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop! Butchie! Siam!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not our captain anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we're gonna kill ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.01,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,W-When did he get behind them?! \NAnd those weapons...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who{\i0} are you going to kill?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He snuck...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...behind us!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! The Pussy Foot Maneuver...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pussy Foot Maneuver?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I do feel a bit of sluggishness.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's handling them like kids,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}after they had the upper hand \Nagainst Zoro and his one sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.11,0:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That man's "Pussy Foot Maneuver" \Nis a silent movement technique.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.11,0:06:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even a group of 50 assassins would \Nbe killed before sensing him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.37,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way we can escape his plan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.20,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I got chills after seeing that \Nhabit of his again three years after!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.75,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His odd way of lifting his glasses \Nto avoid cutting his own face{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with those Cat Claws...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.65,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clear proof that he hasn't \Nforgotten how to fight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I've grown a bit good-natured myself,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.20,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,during my last three years on dry land...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you five minutes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.71,0:07:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't take care of \Nthings here in five minutes...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.26,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I'll kill every last one of you...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes should be enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.66,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Him! If we just beat him, \Nwe can get past this hill!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We had the upper hand against him just now!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cut him up in five minutes!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.46,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Meowban Brothers!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're kicking my swords, too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my "thanks"?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.16,0:08:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! \NThree swords won't help any!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skill's still the same!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.25,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiger...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.34,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...Hunt!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.14,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Four minutes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just having three swords is different
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,from knowing the Three-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One hit...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.76,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He beat the Meowban Brothers in one hit!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.19,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush every last one of you \Nbefore your five minutes are up!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Three minutes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll... slaughter him...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Captain...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hypnotize me...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive. You do sloppy work.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,His tough fat saved him, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get 'im, Butchie!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,More hypnosis?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.99,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy means trouble! \NHe could already crack the ground apart!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens when he's powered up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta wake him up while I still can!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that crafty girl up to now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.61,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's seriously hurt, \Nand he's just sleeping!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Look out!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.22,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Two minutes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Look out!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Split in two!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodge it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.30,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A chakram! \NIt wasn't just a hypnosis tool?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.09,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! How dare you stomp on my face?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's alive?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.36,0:13:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't tell if he has bad or good timing...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Luffy...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.67,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's alive again!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes is impossible now!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.52,0:14:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! That hurts, you jerk!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That wasn't me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me-
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.70,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nami! Did you hurt your shoulder?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing. I'm fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.91,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done everything I can for now, \Nso I leave the rest to you...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.51,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We absolutely can't afford to lose this fight...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For the treasure!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all work out in the end!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.60,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Try hard! For my treasure!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That sounds like you, alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.36,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Captain Jango and Butchie-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.62,0:14:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...can finish them in one minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Butchie! There's no time to think!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill that {\i1}haramaki{\i0} bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.23,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll handle that weird kid...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.75,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time for everyone to die now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That bad butler is here too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he fall off that cliff and die?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't approach me...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...from behind!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaya... What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.54,0:16:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you may not accept my apology,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just couldn't believe it...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Klahadore, a pirate...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Never mind that! \NWhy are you here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I told you to run away!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.09,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is in danger!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.42,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But {\i1}you're{\i0} fighting!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.72,0:17:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after I treated you so horribly \Nand you've been hurt so much,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.64,0:17:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you're still fighting for me! So I...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop this...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this, Klahadore!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.08,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry told me everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the girl from the mansion?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.29,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning she's the plan's final target?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no need to go to the village now?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to kill her, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.27,0:18:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore, please! \NIf you want my fortune, you can have it all!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.73,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please leave this village! Right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.83,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will gladly accept it... but...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.49,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's one other thing I want, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...is peace of mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.55,0:18:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I want simple peace.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.43,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I find the villagers' trust that I've \Nfostered these past three years
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.60,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to be nice and comfortable now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.27,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to have that peace of mind forever...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.87,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I {\i1}will{\i0} have that peace! \N{\i1}And{\i0} your fortune...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.08,0:19:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, pirates {\i1}will{\i0} come to the village!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.01,0:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...you will leave your will and die!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.43,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,These two things are absolute.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're not...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run away, Kaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.69,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use talking to him! Run away!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.82,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're not Klahadore. \NYou're not Klahadore...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.24,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.25,0:19:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this village!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.10,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... You'd point a gun at me...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.26,0:20:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You've certainly grown \Na lot these past three years...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...Miss Kaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.73,0:20:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember? \NSo much has happened in three years...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.23,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent so much time together,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,even before your parents passed \Naway and you became bedridden...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So much time...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So many memories... \NTogether we suffered...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.38,0:20:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Together we rejoiced...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Klahadore...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I would visit the city with you,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and whenever you had a fever, \NI constantly looked after you...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.14,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You listened to my stories so happily...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I devoted myself to you...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For so long...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.32,0:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for so long, I endured it...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.87,0:21:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was all so that I could kill you today...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.55,0:21:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I, a man once known as Captain Kuro,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.90,0:21:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,had to smile humbly for some snot-nosed girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.10,0:21:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I went against my nature \Nand sucked up to you...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.86,0:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.81,0:21:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand these daily insults?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.32,0:21:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand this man \Nonce known as Captain Kuro?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.13,0:22:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.84,0:22:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...I still owe you for hitting me...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.36,0:22:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit me with all your might, as I recall...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.13,0:22:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hate getting hit that much, \NI got a hundred more punches for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:23:03.36,ED1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Chisana koro ni wa takara no chizu ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:10.32,ED1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Atama no naka ni ukandeite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:17.29,ED1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Itsudemo sagashita kiseki no basho o
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:24.46,ED1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Shiranai dareka ni makenai you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:37.18,ED1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Yume sae tsukamenai mama
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:45.65,ED1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Moshi mo sekai ga kawaru no nara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:52.70,ED1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Nanimo shiranai koro no watashi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:24:05.71,ED1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Tsurete itte omoide ga iro asenai you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:23:03.36,ED1-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}When I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:10.32,ED1-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}I had a vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:17.29,ED1-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}and I always searched for that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:24.46,ED1-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}before someone else could beat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:37.18,ED1-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:45.65,ED1-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:52.70,ED1-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}then take me to the time when I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:24:05.71,ED1-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.34,0:24:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! You go save Miss Kaya! \NLeave the bad butler to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.47,0:24:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a helplessly evil guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.31,0:24:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan to help him, though!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.77,0:24:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm goin' after that hypno-freak!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.35,0:24:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro! You're not cut out to be a pirate!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.27,0:24:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My ambition is much greater than yours!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.19,0:24:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.82,0:24:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat Kuro! \NUsopp the Man's Tearful Resolve!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.32,0:24:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:36.09,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,115)}Beat Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:36.09,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,460)}Usopp the Man's Tearful Resolve!
